  "statement": "The app MUST NOT silently fail.. Every send either visibly succeeds or visibly fails; there is no state in which the founder believes a message was delivered when it was not. This includes resume/spawn: if a session cannot be resumed or spawned, the failure is visible and the message is not shown as delivered. (Encodes FR-19.)",
